programme.title: World Watch: Rise of The Machine Ep11
programme.desc: Dokumentari yang mendedahkan ciptaan paling mengejutkan yang menjadikan mesin terbesar dan paling ikonik. Episod kali ini membawa penonton melihat inovasi yang terdapat pada HSS Saint Paul John II yang merupakan feri jenis catamaran kedua terbesar di dunia. Feri super yang beroperasi di lautan Mediterranean dengan kelajuan sehingga 69km/j ini menghubungkan kepulauan Malta dan Sicily, Itali. Dengan Panjang 110M, feri super ini mampu memuatkan 1,100 penumpang dan 167 kenderaan penumpang dalam satu-satu masa tanpa mengabaikan aspek-aspek keselamatan dengan teknologi yang canggih.

programme.title: Bidadari: Mimpi Yang Sempurna Ep12
programme.desc: Wardah, pembantu kepada Haiman yang berwatak panas baran, berubah sikap selepas mendapat nasihat dan mereka menjadi rapat. Selepas lima tahun, Wardah bertemu Haiman semula dalam kes hak penjagaan anaknya. Walaupun menghadapi konflik dengan Arissa dan Zaki, Wardah dan Haiman akhirnya berkahwin, namun mereka terus menghadapi cabaran dalam hubungan dan keluarga, termasuk tragedi yang tak terduga. Haiman luahkan perasaan ke? Wardah masih tidak boleh lupakan peristiwa 5 tahun Haiman menghilang! Akim pula betul-betul nak tahu tentang Haiman! Pelakon: Aqasha, Tiz Zaqyah, Farahdhiya, Keith Foo, Elisha Sandha, Afifah Nasir, Shaharuddin Thamby, Arash Mohamad, Kuna, Aidil Aziz, Firdaus Ghufran, Rania Humaira, Jesse Lim, Ramli Salleh, dan Elanie Aidid.

programme.title: Cuit-Cuit: Misi Dania Cun Ep11
programme.desc: Dania, seorang Jururawat Desa, menerima tugas dipedalaman selepas dipujuk ayahnya. Di klinik, dia berhadapan dengan cabaran seperti bertentangan dengan bomoh Pak Landak dan menjalin hubungan rapat dengan Dr. Dani, yang menimbulkan cemburu Misi Ilya. Sikap rajin dan kecantikannya membuatkan Dania digelar "Misi Dania Cun" oleh penduduk desa. Marah sungguh Iliya dengan Pakcik Kasim. Cerewet sangat bila diminta buat pemeriksaan kesihatan, tapi kalau dengan Misi Dania senang sahaja dia berurusan. Misi Dania dapat cek bernilai 10 ribu?! Pelakon: Niena Baharun, Dazrin Kamarudin, Livonia Ricky, Aemma Nursyakira, Jibob, Ziema Din, Rostan Man, Hasnol, Hafiz Bahari, Yujie Mazlina, Mas Khan, Z. Lokman, Kamarool Hj. Yusof, dan Ben Konobie.

programme.title: Spektra: Kau? C.E.O Aku? Ep2
programme.desc: Aisya berkahwin dengan Danial atas pilihan keluarga, namun perkahwinan mereka terganggu akibat kehadiran Mila, teman rapat Danial. Setelah kehilangan anak, Danial memutuskan untuk berkahwin dengan Mila, sementara Aisya terpaksa menerima keputusan itu. Namun, Aisya mendapat sokongan teman-temannya, Anis, Syafiq, dan Hakimi, yang berusaha memperjuangkan haknya. Danial yang tidak setuju dengan cadangan ibu bapanya yang mahu dia berkahwin dengan Aisya. Akhirnya Danial bersetuju kerana tidak mahu jawatan CEO nya dilucutkan. Pelakon: Azrel Ismail, Puteri Aishah, Syazwan Zulkifly, Neera Azizi, Talha Harith, Siti Hariesa, Trisha Ooi, Zuhairi Ibrahim, Anne Abdullah, Amelina, Ainina Ahmad, dan Zalfa Zin

programme.title: Panorama Ep15
programme.desc: Panorama memaparkan 2 segmen menarik iaitu Serunai Kedah dan Ubi telampong. Serunai Kedah merupakan alatan muzik tradisional yang masih mendapat tempat dan peminat di negeri Kedah manakala manisan Ubi Telampong semakin pupus ditelan zaman. Usaha-usaha dijalankan oleh Dr. Jazliza Jamaluddin dan Dr. Fitri Yusof serta penduduk Kampung Bukit Beruas, Jitra, Kedah bagi melestarikan manisan ini.

Pergaduhan terjadi lagi dan Daus bertindak kasar lagi terhadap Mia. Lyssa cuba menahan Daus tetapi kakinya tiba2 lemah dan dia jatuh. Lyssa dikejarkan ke hospital. Berita kehamilan Lyssa tidak dapat mengimbangi kemarahan Daus terhadap kecurangan Mia. Lyssa sedih kerana tidak diberi perhatian yang sewajarnya dari Daus. Mia yang banyak menghabiskan masa membantu dan menguruskan Lyssa.

programme.title: 25 Nabi Ep4
programme.desc: Episod kali ini menceritakan mengenai kisah Nabi Hud a.s . Penceritaan akan bermula dari pendahuluan sehinggalah kisah-kisah yang berkaitan dengan peristiwa yang membawa kepada contoh dan teladan bagi umat Islam.

programme.title: Elhan Untuk Nian
programme.desc: Kematian mengejut Ashman dalam usia muda membuatkan Nian jadi terkejut dan hilang arah diri. Norman mahu kahwinkan Nian dengan Elhan yang merupakan pekerja di kandang kambing. Nian tidak setuju kerana Elhan sangat kolot dan tidak layak baginya. Kematian mengejut Suraya dan Norman pula lumpuh buat Nian terpaksa akur pada cadangan abahnya. Bermula sebuah pernikahan yang bukan demi cinta. Nian tetap dengan ego dan memperlekehkan Elhan. Dia tetap anggap Elhan hanya kulinamun Elhan selalu senyum dan sabar.

programme.title: Puji Pujian & Kalam Allah V1
programme.desc: Zikir dan bacaan surah-surah lazim.

programme.title: Salam Nusantara Pulau Jawa Ep4
programme.desc: Salam Nusantara membawa semua ke kota yang ketiga terbesar di Indonesia iaitu Bandung. Suasana di Bandung berlainan sedikit dengan kota-kota lain di Indonesia kerana disini udaranya lebih nyaman dan sejuk. Ini adalah kerana kota ini terletak di kawasan pergunungan yang tingginya lebih kurang 1000 meter di atas paras laut. Selain itu, Bandung ialah pusat pendidikan tinggi Indonesia. Namun factor ekonomi menjadi tarikan utama, dimana Bandung adalah syurga beli-belah dan barangan runcit borong.

programme.title: Religious Clip S70 Ep3
programme.desc: Dalam episod kali ini, topik yang di sampaikan ialah Hormat dan Sayang. Nabi pernah bersabda bukan dari golongan kami kepada mereka yang tidak sayang dan hormat kepada orang yang tua. Bersama Ustaz Safwan yang akan mengupas lebih lanjut mengenai topik yang menarik ini.

programme.title: Setia Menunggumu Ep5
programme.desc: Ramlan sering mengingatkan Adi supaya jangan ganggu Aida lagi kerana dia akan bertunang dengan Aida. Tetapi Adi telah bertanyakan sendiri kepada Aida, benarkah dia akan bertunang dengan Ramlan, Aida telah memberikan jawapan tidak. Adi terlihat Ramlan menjual dadah kepada budak-budak kampung, lalu dia melaporkan perkara ini kepada pihak polis. Ramlan telah menyerang Adi kerana Adi masih rapat lagi dengan Aida, tiba-tiba waktu itu datang sepasukan polis. Kenapakah polis datang kepada mereka? Apakah yang terjadi kepada mereka?

programme.title: Jalan Lain Menuju Surga
programme.desc: Yosan dan Dadang merupakan penjual tepi jalan dan mereka berniaga bersama serta berjiran hanya bersebelahan rumah. Yosan mengesyaki Dadang seorang pencuri kerana rezeki yang tidak putus-putus melimpahi dirinya walaupun dia hanya seorang penjual tepi jalan. Namun, semua itu merupakan salah faham.

Dakwah bukan sekadar untuk bercakap tetapi menjadi ikon mempunyai akhlak yang baik dan orang lain mencontohi kita juga merupakan satu dakwah. Bersama Ustazah Hidayu yang akan membincangkan topik ini dengan lebih lanjut lagi.

Akibat terkejut dengan apa yang dibongkarkan, Tengku Kamal yang menghidap sakit jantung meninggal dunia. Tengku Zahara tidak dapat menerima kenyataan dan menjadi murung. programme.title: Rumput Tetangga
programme.desc: Cerita berpusat pada Kirana (dilakonkan oleh Titi Kamal), seorang suri rumah yang dahulunya adalah pelajar popular dan cemerlang di sekolah. Namun, selepas berkahwin dengan Ben (Raffi Ahmad) dan mempunyai dua anak, Kirana mula merasa tidak yakin diri dan bosan dengan kehidupannya sebagai suri rumah. programme.title: Araf 5

Zeynep, seorang wanita muda, kecewa apabila dia mengetahui bahawa bekas teman lelakinya Kadir membunuhnya dengan cara digantung. Bagaimanapun, tiada apa yang dilihat di dalam rumah itu menggambarkan kebenaran. Dalam proses ini, Zeynep mengetahui tentang kematian Kadir daripada entiti yang menghantui rumah itu. Diseret ke dalam pusaran, Zeynep mendapati dirinya di tengah-tengah Api Penyucian, tempat antara dua alam.

programme.desc: Mengisahkan Mika, Khai dan Iris dikejar polis. Mereka berjaya menyembunyikan diri dalam salah sebuah kedai motorsikal dan menawan seluruh pekerja kedai itu. Setelah membukanya, Khai mendapati beg itu mengandungi bungkusan coklat yang dibalut dengan kertas warna keemasan. Kemudian pasukan polis berjaya mengempung lokasi persembunyian mereka. Que yang turut ditahan polis, dibawa bersama untuk memujuk kawan-kawannya menyerah diri.

Apabila Rachel mula mengalami halusinasi mengenai ibu mereka yang sudah meninggal dan sesuatu artifak purba, petunjuk-petunjuk menakutkan mula terbongkar mengenai masa lalu keluarga mereka.

Di KL, Uzair bertemu semula dengan Ajeeb yang kini menjadi busker jalanan dan tinggal di bawah jambatan. Hatta datang untuk melawan Uzair di gelanggang haram untuk menyelesaikan hutang lama.

programme.title: Alam Puaka Ep3

programme.title: Abang Long Fadil 1
programme.desc: Abang Long Fadil, seorang lelaki yang sentiasa berangan bahawa kehidupannya seperti seorang gangster. Namun, apabila sahabat baiknya, Malik, dimasukkan ke penjara, keadaan menjadi lebih huru-hara, dan angan-angannya mungkin tidak jauh daripada realiti.

programme.title: Bini-bini Ku Gangster
programme.desc: Manja dan Herry adalah sepasang suami isteri yang sangat romantik dan saling sayang menyayangi. Tanpa disedari oleh Herry, Manja adalah ketua kumpulan kepada sebuah geng gengster di Kuala Lumpur. Di pejabat,Herry kerap dibuli Mat Saja termasuk menyuruh Herry menggantikan tempatnya semasa ulangtahun perkahwinan Manja dan Herry yang ke2. Manja bengang lalu menghantar orang-orangnya memukul Mat Saja.

programme.title: Wangi
programme.desc: Nor dan suaminya, Khuzairi tinggal di sebuah banglo bersama dua anak mereka. Selepas melahirkan anak kedua, Nor pulang ke rumah dan ibunya datang untuk menjaganya. Dia perasan bahawa pembantu rumahnya, Bella telah hilang. Bella seperti adik kepada Nor dan dia tinggal bersama mereka. Suaminya mengatakan bahawa Bella telah kembali ke Amsterdam untuk berkahwin. Nor mengesyaki dan tidak lama kemudian anak-anaknya mula mempunyai kelakuan luar biasa. Anak pertama mereka suka bercakap dengan dirinya sendiri dan tidur di tempat yang rawak; suaminya menyembunyikan rahsia manakala seorang wanita tua sentiasa memberi amaran kepada Nor. Tanpa disedari oleh Nor, Bella yang hilang mungkin sedang mengintai di sudut gelap banglo itu.

programme.title: Rampok
programme.desc: Seorang wanita bersenjata merompak bank dan menjadikan mereka yang berada dalam bank sebagai orang tebusan. Pihak polis berunding dan wanita tersebut bersetuju untuk melepaskan tebusan tanpa pihak polis mengetahui bahawa orang tebusan tersebut merupakan perompak dan rakan perompak itu sendiri.

programme.title: Perempuan Bergaun Merah
programme.desc: Sejak sahabat baiknya hilang, hidup Dinda berubah menjadi mimpi ngeri apabila satu roh jahat yang berupa wanita berbaju merah menghantui dirinya. Dinda terancam bukan hanya oleh roh jahat itu, tetapi juga oleh individu yang cuba menyembunyikan kejadian malam kehilangan sahabatnya.

programme.title: Ong Bak: Muay Thai Warriors
programme.desc: Apabila kepala patung yang suci di sebuah kampung dicuri, seorang ahli seni mempertahankan diri pergi ke bandar besar dan mendapati dirinya mengambil dunia bawah tanah untuk mendapatkannya.

programme.title: Cinderella's Curse
programme.desc: Cinderella, dalam keadaan terdesak, memanggil ibu pari-parinya melalui sebuah kitab kuno yang terikat dengan kulit manusia, dengan harapan untuk menuntut keadilan dan membalas dendam terhadap ibu tiri dan kakak tirinya yang sentiasa menyeksa serta menindasnya tanpa henti.

programme.title: Adnan Sempit 3
programme.desc: Menyaksikan Adnan berkahwin dengan cinta zaman kanak-kanaknya, Nadia, manakala Bobby pula berkahwin dengan Wawa. Adnan juga semakin mahir menguruskan perniagaannya sendiri. Walau bagaimanapun, kedua-dua pasangan ini segera menyedari bahawa perkahwinan bukan sekadar berkongsi rumah bersama seseorang, tetapi lebih daripada itu.

programme.title: Ong Bak 2
programme.desc: Berlatarkan Thailand abad ke-15, filem ini berkisarkan Tien, anak kepada seorang bangsawan yang dibunuh. Ditawan dan dijual sebagai hamba, Tien diselamatkan daripada kematian oleh Chernang, ketua Pha Beek Khrut, sekumpulan artis mempertahankan diri yang pakar dalam pelbagai gaya tempur Asia.

programme.title: Black S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Sebagai tukaran dengan fail ayahnya, Lokman memujuk Sofia untuk bekerja dengannya dan menggunakan kuasa Sofia untuk memberitahunya mana-mana kliennya yang akan menemui ajal. Semasa menjalankan tugas, Sofia bertemu Black yang menyedari kuasa Sofia mungkin kunci untuk membantunya memburu 419. Namun, caranya yang kasar menjengkelkan Sofia dan dia mendapati dirinya tidak diendahkan. Demi memenangi semula hati Sofia, Black menyiasat kes tembakan yang melibatkan Malik untuk meyakinkan Sofia yang dia bukan punca Malik ditembak. Pendirian Sofia berubah menjadi agak lembut dan seterusnya bersetuju untuk membantu Black mendapatkan ingatannya semula. Namun keadaan menjadi rumit apabila Black mengungkai lebih banyak petunjuk tentang kematian Malik dan menyedari nyawanya dalam bahaya.

programme.title: Din Tiger Ep2
programme.desc: Sepuluh tahun kemudian, Din dibebaskan dari penjara dengan satu misi dalam fikirannya membawa keluar anaknya, Elyn, yang kini dalam genggaman Big Boss Mario. Tetapi tugas ini jauh lebih sukar daripada yang disangkanya.

Sementara itu Dr. Rizman cuba berbincang dengan isteri mengenai anak tunggalnya, Khai, setelah dia mendapati Khai sudah tersasar jauh daripada keluarga. Dr.Rizman juga mengakui dia telah mengabaikan tanggung jawabnya terhadap Khai. programme.desc: Daniel dan Cynthia, pasangan muda dengan anak dalam perjalanan, mengalami masa sukar di Manila. Mereka kembali ke Baguio, tempat asal Daniel, untuk memulakan semula. Melalui kebaikan Alex, kawan Daniel zaman kanak-kanak yang kaya, mereka dapat tinggal di sebuah rumah besar, tanpa sewa; dan dia mendapat tawaran kerja juga. Segala-galanya seolah-olah jatuh pada tempatnya untuk mereka - atau begitulah yang mereka fikirkan - sehingga perkara aneh mula berlaku di rumah mereka.

programme.title: Superbike
programme.desc: Ia berkisar tentang kehidupan seharian sekumpulan penunggang motosikal superbike yang menggelar kumpulan mereka sebagai 'Pirate Bikers' dan diketuai oleh Bugs (Kamal Adli). Berlumba-lumba di jalanan, kejar-mengejar, berkonvoi dan disaman oleh polis telah menjadi rasa masam dalam kehidupan mereka yang berkongsi minat yang sama.

programme.title: Jwanita
programme.desc: Jwanita (Maya Karin) yang sakit mental dan didera oleh Ibu / Dukun (Umie Aida) dan bapa angkatnya (Radin Intan), yang mengamalkan ilmu hitam. Jwanita kemudian bertemu dengan Farhan (Bront Palarae) yang menjaganya selepas dia membunuh kedua ibu bapa angkatnya dalam satu peristiwa tragis.

programme.title: Plan B Ep10
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Khai, Iris, Mika dan Que terlibat dalam satu rompakan. Mereka merompak sebuah van syarikat keselamatan milik bapa Mika, Yusof, yang membawa sejumlah wang besar. Mereka bertembung dengan kumpulan yang diketuai oleh King. Dalam aksi tembak menembak antara kedua-dua kumpulan, kesemua pengawal keselamatan yang mengiringi wang itu, ditembak mati oleh King. Mika juga cedera ditembak. Dalam aksi kejar mengejar antara dua kumpulan itu dan tembak menembak, King dan orang-orangnya mati ditembak oleh Khai, ketika berjaya membawa lari wang rompakan itu. Di pejabat keselamatan, Yusof dapat menyaksi aksi rompakan itu melalui kamera tertutup dan mendapati anaknya, Mika ditembak.

programme.title: Din Tiger Ep3
programme.desc: Din Tiger berusaha mencari kebenaran di sebalik kematian isterinya, tetapi keadaan bertambah rumit akibat penyelewengan yang dilakukan oleh Anat terbongkar.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep3
programme.desc: Apabila Uzair pulang ke rumah untuk bersama adik dan ibunya, dia dihalau oleh ibunya yang tidak mahu dia tinggal bersama mereka. Uzair mendapattahu bahawa Ashikin telah disimpan oleh Imran dan dia pergi untuk menyelamatkannya. Apabila Ashikin menyuruh melupakannya, Uzair kecewa dan pergi ke bandar.

programme.title: Two Sisters
programme.desc: Selepas seorang gadis dibebaskan dari rumah sakit jiwa, dia disatukan semula dengan kakaknya dan mereka kembali ke rumah keluarga yang ditinggalkan. Namun, kedua-dua beradik itu menyimpan rahsia gelap dan tragis keluarga yang mula terungkap selepas kepulangan mereka.

programme.title: Bujang Selamat
programme.desc: Sering diganggu budak-budak di kampung, Bujang mula mempelajari ilmu persilatan. Bujang pergi mendaftarkan diri untuk bertanding di satu pertandingan silat namun telah diperli budak-budak lain. Rasa terhina, Bujang pun pergi bertemu seorang guru silat. Bersama guru itu, Bujang mempelajari teknik bersilat yang sangat hebat.

programme.title: Tembus
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang lelaki bernama Hari yang memegang tanggungjawab besar dalam mengotakan janji agar kehidupan rumahtangganya menjadi semakin baik. Di mata masyarakat, Hari dan isterinya, Izza dianggap sebagai pasangan ideal yang sukses dalam hal rumahtangga dan kerjaya. Namun mereka diuji dengan kehilangan anak dan pelbagai rahsia terbongkar akibat terjadinya peristiwa itu.

programme.title: Azura
programme.desc: Seorang jejaka yang berasal daripada keluarga orang berada ingin mengahwini wanita pilihannya, Azura namun ditentang ibu bapanya. Zack mengahwini Azura dan bekerja sebagai buruh untuk menyara keluarganya - ini setelah kewangannya dipotong oleh keluarga. Azura hamil namun dia mula mengesyaki bahawa bayi tersebut bukan miliknya.

programme.title: Satu Impian
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Indra yang berhasrat untuk bekerja di bandar untuk membantu ibunya yang telah tua. Setelah mendapat restu ibunya, Indra mencari pekerjaan di bandar dengan bertemu Dato Karim rakan baik arwah bapanya. Indra diterima bekerja dan diminta untuk tinggal di rumah Dato Karim. Pada mulanya kehadiran Indra tidak disenangi Sandra, anak Dato Karim. Namun hubungan mereka semakin baik selepas Indra menyelamatkan Sandra daripada samseng jalanan. Pada masa yang sama, terdapat satu gerakan yang ingin mensabotaj projek yang sedang diuruskan syarikat Dato Karim.

programme.title: Azura (2012)
programme.desc: Azura, seorang gadis remaja yang gigih hadapi cabaran hidup untuk mencapai cita-citanya. Dia tinggal bersama ibu saudaranya setelah kedua ibu bapanya meninggal dunia dalam satu tragedi. Azura kemudiannya menjadi mahasiswa di sebuah universiti swasta dan menjalinkan hubungan mesra dengan Zek, seorang anak hartawan. Walau bagaimanapun, cinta mereka dihalang oleh bapa Zek dan mereka terpaksa melalui pelbagai dugaan.

programme.title: Bila Jodoh
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang lelaki bernama Hasrul yang selalu gagal mencari jodoh untuk dirinya. Dengan secara tidak sengaja, dia sering bertemu Liza namun mereka sering bertikam lidah. Dalam masa yang sama, keluarga Hasrul mencari calon untuk dijodohkan dengannya. Tanpa disedari Hasrul, gadis yang ingin dikenalkan kepadanya ialah Liza.

programme.title: XX Ray
programme.desc: Obsesinya terhadap angkasa lepas telah membuatkan Amir untuk mencipta sebuah topi keledar. Topi keledar ini merupakan penemuan baru apabila ia menggunakan kuasa tahi bintang. Sesiapa sahaja yang memakainya boleh melihat menembusi apa sahaja yang mereka inginkan. Kekacauan berlaku apabila topi itu telah menyebabkan Amir bertukar menjadi halimunan.

programme.title: Kau,Aku Dan Dia
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Nancy dan Syafiq yang baru tamat pengajian di universiti. Walaupun berlainan bangsa, namun mereka saling mencintai antara satu sama lain. Konflik mula berlaku apabila orang tua ingin menjodohkan mereka dengan orang lain. Syafiq kemudiannya bertemu dengan seorang gadis buta bernama Mastura yang dilanggarnya secara tidak sengaja. Semakin hari, hubungan antara Syafiq dan Mastura menjadi semakin rapat sehingga Nancy berasa tersisih.

programme.title: XX Ray 2
programme.desc: Bekerja sebagai saintis kadet, Tina berasa ditipu apabila Johan mendakwa dia yang mencipta mesin pelupusan laser walhal ia merupakan hasil cetusan idea dari Tina. Ingin menghalang niat jahat Johan, Tina meminta bantuan Amir. Namun, keduanya terkena pancaran laser mesin itu dalam cubaan untuk menghalang Johan dan telah dihantar ke zaman Kesultanan Melayu Melaka.

Ramlan sendiri beranggapan bahawa dengan berlaku sombong terhadap orang, dirinya akan dipandang mulia. programme.title: XX Ray

Sesiapa sahaja yang memakainya boleh melihat menembusi apa sahaja yang mereka inginkan. Kekacauan berlaku apabila topi itu telah menyebabkan Amir bertukar menjadi halimunan.

programme.title: Bila Jodoh
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang lelaki bernama Hasrul yang selalu gagal mencari jodoh untuk dirinya. Dengan secara tidak sengaja, dia sering bertemu Liza namun mereka sering bertikam lidah. Dalam masa yang sama, keluarga Hasrul mencari calon untuk dijodohkan dengannya. Tanpa disedari Hasrul, gadis yang ingin dikenalkan kepadanya ialah Liza.

programme.title: Bujang Selamat

programme.title: Kau,Aku Dan Dia

programme.desc: Five young professionals with different life skills, team up for two days and one night trip, leading the audiance to explore the good life of nature and the beauty of the land of Taiwan.5

programme.title: Way to Health M Ep333
programme.desc: This show invites top medical professionals from different fields to answer questions from the audience. Approved by the medical world, this show is an influential, as well as reliable place to understand more about ones health.

programme.title: Way to Health M Ep334
programme.desc: This show invites top medical professionals from different fields to answer questions from the audience. Approved by the medical world, this show is an influential, as well as reliable place to understand more about ones health.

programme.title: Top Singers T Ep652
programme.desc: The show Top Singers aims to spotlight outstanding Taiwanese singers and composers, setting a new standard in the industry. Combining elements of competition, variety, and personal stories, the show welcomes participants of all ages. Its goals include discovering grassroots talent, innovating Taiwanese song performance styles, and involving more local talent in song composition to infuse new life into Taiwanese music.

programme.title: Show Biz M Ep1006
programme.desc: Every second counts in Show Biz to bring you with the most High Speed star news, exciting live shows and performers interviews.

programme.title: Dear Mom M Ep38
programme.desc: FengYi Li handles everything in the house while her husband, ShuAn, lounges and daydreams. She constantly worries about the love lives of their four daughters. YiWan starts a relationship with a gang leaders son despite claiming to have never dated. QingQing may be having an affair with a married man. XiaoXi is infatuated with the school team captain but is unaware of the others. AnQing returns from the US with her son after a failed marriage. When FengYi suddenly disappears, the sisters realize theyve neglected their mother, who has always supported them. Now they must find her and get their lives back on track.

programme.title: All U Need is Love
programme.desc: Ten major film companies join forces on a comedy-drama film to raise funds and create jobs for industry workers during the COVID-19 pandemic. This film features an all-star ensemble cast starring for free, with the story revolving around a group of hotel guests placed under quarantine in Hong Kong.

programme.title: Time Still Turns the Pages
programme.desc: High school teacher Cheng recalls his violent childhood memories when he finds an anonymous suicide note in the classroom. While he has to prevent the tragedy involving a suicidal student from happening, he also has to face a series of family problems with his wife wanting to divorce him and his fathers serious illness.

programme.title: Wolf Pack
programme.desc: The Wolf Pack squad led by Lao Diao, is a foreign-based team that specializes in overseas security jobs. In one of the missions, the squad discovers that a terrorist force is planning to destroy the countrys energy source. Lao Diao is now entrusted with the task of leading his squad to fight back. Can the Wolf Pack save the day?

programme.title: Fagara
programme.desc: After her fathers death, a Hong Kong girl discovers she has two hitherto unknown sisters, Branch and Cherry. Through taking up her late fathers hotpot restaurant, she reunites with her sisters by different mothers, and understands her father more from a different perspective, allowing her to finally resolve her long-time hard feelings with him.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon (2020)
programme.desc: In 1960s Hong Kong, rookie cop Xu Le cracks a robbery but gets demoted instead, as this offends a corrupt inspector. Xu meets a rich girl Bai who falls instantly in love with him one day. Will he break up with his childhood girlfriend for Bai so as to climb the social ladder, and how does Xu eventually become one of Hong Kongs legendary detective?

programme.title: Everything Under Control
programme.desc: During a diamond heist, one of the security escorts, Jelly, steals the diamonds and flees. Fellow security escorts, Yau Shing and Penguin, are forced to help the robber track down the diamonds. They stumble onto a remote village along the way, encountering strange villagers and mysterious incidents. Can they finally locate Jelly and the diamonds?

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: Initial D
programme.desc: The movie is adapted from a famous Japanese manga. 18-year-old Takumi delivers tofu in his father's near-obsolete car every day and becomes a good racer with perfect drifting skill. Encouraged by his father, he joins a mountain race and unexpectedly wins it, making him famous overnight and leading him from one exciting race to another.

programme.title: The Rescue
programme.desc: An emergency occurs on an offshore drilling rig that would cause it to capsize and sink. The Emergency Response Unit races against the clock in a chopper rescue mission amidst dangerous explosions and fire. Captain Gao Qian must work seamlessly with his chopper pilot Zhao Cheng to rescue survivors using the most maverick and dangerous tactics.

programme.title: In Broad Daylight
programme.desc: Based on a true event of a news investigative unit receiving a tip-off about the abuse of residents in an Elderly and Disabled Care Home. To expose the homes wrongdoings, reporter Kay goes undercover to expose the inhumanity and unveil the cruel truth under broad daylight.

programme.title: YUM Investigation
programme.desc: YUM is a detective agency that handles supernatural cases. As YUM investigates the evil spirits appearing in an old building, they discover that the spirits are created by a spirit master to haunt the residents so that the building can be vacated for redevelopment. Can the YUM investigators finally find ways to fight against the master?

programme.title: The Moon Thieves
programme.desc: A crooked watch dealer assembles a daring crew - a thief, an explosive expert, a lock breaker and a watch connoisseur - to steal three luxury watches in Tokyo. Their mission takes an unexpected turn when they discover the legendary 'Moonwatch.' Pursued by the yakuza, the team must unite to navigate the chaos and pull off their high-stakes heist.

programme.title: American Girl
programme.desc: 13 year-old Fen is uprooted from LA and moves to Taipei in early 2003, when her mother is diagnosed with breast cancer. She struggles to adjust to her new life with a new school and long-separated father, and drifts away from her mother. When her younger sister is misdiagnosed with SARS, they finally open up to each other during quarantine.

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 1
programme.desc: Wu Dang Sects Zhang Chui Shans son, Zhang Wu Ji, finds himself accidentally embroiled in the fight for the Dragon Sabre. When he unwittingly learns the powerful martial arts skills from the Jiuyin scriptures, Wu Ji proceeds to help the Six Major sects fight against the corrupt government.

programme.title: Secret Diary of a Mom To Be, The
programme.desc: A high-flying PR manager and her loving husband swear by a childless lifestyle but she is shocked to learn that she is expecting just when things look bright for a promotion! How would they deal with the unexpected surprises that life throws in their way?

programme.title: Infernal Affairs III
programme.desc: Ming is transferred to do menial police work ten months after the murder of Yan, in 2004. Meanwhile, a new star, Wing, has emerged in the police force and Ming suspects he is also a mole sent by the triad. Determined to start anew, Ming must kill Wing while ensuring his own identity does not get exposed.

programme.title: Princess and 7 Kung Fu Masters
programme.desc: Seven Kung Fu masters live in Lucky Town, the only safe residing place in northeast China. When warlord Lam refuses to side with the Japanese, an agent is assigned to take over his army and kill his daughter using ninjutsu. Lams daughter escapes and seeks help from the seven masters, who finally defeat the enemy and save the warlord!

programme.title: One More Chance
programme.desc: Chow Yun Fat stars as a down-on-his-luck gambler, Water, whose ex-girlfriend asked him to take care of their autistic son. As Water lives with his son, he soon finds his goal in life. When he discovers his sons talent in running, Water decides to give up his dissipated life and support his son to achieve his dream.

programme.title: Endless Battle
programme.desc: This is a story about two brothers. The younger brother is a drug lord while the elder brother Zhong is a police officer in the Narcotics Bureau. Both are involved in a drug cartels turf battle and during an escort mission, Zhong discovers his brothers hidden identity. This leads to an endless battle between good and evil.

programme.title: Kung Fu Dunk
programme.desc: Shi Jie grew up in a martial arts school and possesses an extraordinary shooting skill. Street hustler Chen Li sees his talent and arranges for him to join a university basketball team. With his kung fu dunking skill, Shi Jie manages to win all college basketball matches, bringing him wealth and also strengthening his relationship with Chen Li.

programme.title: Z Storm
programme.desc: ICAC Chief Officer Luk is on the case of a corrupt policeman but finds all key witnesses killed when he starts to discover some clues. As investigation continues, Luk uncovers the fraud scheme of an organized corrupt group involving the governments $15 billion Care Fund. He must fight against them to keep Hong Kong corruption free.

programme.title: The Phantom Lover
programme.desc: In 1926 China, Sung, a talented singer, is deeply in love with To, a sweet innocent girl from a wealthy family. Their love evokes strong disapproval from To's father and bitter jealousy from her designated fianc, a young man chosen by her family. This is a story about a singer and a wealthy girl battling to be together in a traditional community.

programme.title: One and Only
programme.desc: Veteran street dancer Ding Lei, invites passionate street dancer, Chen Shuo to his dance club. Sparks fly when Chen dances with the clubs top dancers. Chen pursues his dream to perform but discovers that Ding has invited him for another reason. As both of them deal with hard times, can they turn the tide on the challenges that they are facing?

programme.title: Lonely Eighteen
programme.desc: Set in the 1980s Hong Kong, Elaine and her best friend Ying enter the entertainment industry hoping to change their fates from poverty. Ying soon becomes a popular porn star but Elaine is lost between being her true self and an actress. When show business declines after a decade, their choices lead them to two different paths in life.

programme.title: Enter the Fat Dragon
programme.desc: Donnie Yen plays a Hong Kong police officer who is highly skilled in martial arts but balloons to more than 200 pounds after his fianc left him. His boss can only assign simple tasks to him like escorting a criminal to Japan, but can he complete it?

programme.title: Mr & Mrs Gambler
programme.desc: Manfred and Flora are gambling addicts who have come across each other a few times at the casino, but do not leave impression on each other until they both suffer heavy losses and are held hostage by the loan sharks in Macau. They find themselves falling in love, and decide to get married when they come back to Hong Kong.

programme.title: Mr. Long
programme.desc: A Taiwanese hitman Mr. Long escapes from the triad after his assignment in Tokyo gone awry. He encounters a Taiwanese woman and her son and the three of them start a new life together. Unfortunately, Mr. Long is being pursued by the triad again

programme.title: Hidden Heroine
programme.desc: A drug cartel is entrenched in the Dong Zhou area. Mei Jing of the Thunderbolt Womens Commando Unit, leads her team to attack the drug base, but they are being ambushed and the identity of Meis father as an undercover is exposed. After a fierce battle, Mei and her team manage to successfully defeat the drug cartel and rescue her father.

programme.title: Endgame
programme.desc: A killer and a stage actor accidentally swapped their identities at a bathhouse. The actor must complete the killers mission while the killer thinks he is a hopeless actor after losing his memory during the accident. When the killer strives to become a successful stage actor, he also starts to recall what has happened

programme.title: A Witness out of the Blue
programme.desc: The police suspects that a jewel thief, found dead in his unit with all stolen goods missing, is killed by his gang leader. They also found the crime to be related to a jewel robbery many months ago, with the robbers involved being killed off one by one. In this complicated case, the polices only witness is a talking parrot from the crime scene.

programme.title: The Ex-Files 4: Marriage Plan
programme.desc: Two brothers, Meng Yun and Yu Fei, are of marriageable age and are facing challenges in love. Yun dodges family pressure to marry after his breakup, while Fei and his girlfriend opt for a marriage cooling-off period to tackle marriage issues.

programme.title: The Deadly Duo
programme.desc: The prince of the Sung Dynasty is captured by the Chin invaders and is guarded by top martial arts masters. It is up to two powerful patriots to fight the overwhelming odds and pull off the impossible: to rescue the royal Prince and get out of the Chin stronghold alive.

programme.title: Brothers Five
programme.desc: The five Kao brothers, separated since birth, are unaware that the master of Teng Lung Manor has killed their father. All five however, vow to defeat the vicious gangsters at the manor due to their bullying ways. After reuniting and with much discipline and hard work, the Kaos are prepared to face Lung and his gang.

programme.title: Opium And The Kung-Fu Master
programme.desc: Tie Qiao San, head of the Ten Guangdong Tigers, is an honourable master with many disciples. As opium becomes popular among the nobles, Tie starts taking it and gradually harms his body. When an opium houses owner defeats Tie in a fight and he is only saved from being killed by his disciple, Tie vows to quit opium and get back on his feet.

programme.title: The Emperor and his Brother
programme.desc: The Emperor Qianlong is not the legitimate successor to the throne at birth, but he only learns the truth when two senior members of a subversive anti-government secret organisation contact him years later. As it happens, the chef of this organisation is Qianlongs younger brother and they must now confront each other in opposing roles

programme.title: The Master Of Kung Fu
programme.desc: The famous kung fu master Wong Fei Hung teaches martial arts in Guangdong. A vicious gangster plots to harm Wongs disciples and frames him for robbery and murder. Wong has to fight against the culprit to prove his own innocence and take revenge for his disciples.

programme.title: Golden Swallow
programme.desc: A heroine finds herself in a love triangle with a swordsman and a warrior. They team up to conquer the evil forces of the martial arts world but she is unable to choose between both men even as they face a deadly duel.

programme.title: Ambitious Kung Fu Girl
programme.desc: The lovely Michelle Mei Suet plays a spoiled girl Szu-szu who ignores her true love Yang Fan to go off in search of a swordsman Chin Ko she idolizes. The search sets off one great action scene after another, until she's threatened to be sold into slavery but Yang Fan arrives in the nick of time! This amusing and entertaining variation on the standard kung-fu film is definitely a winner.

programme.title: The Three Smiles
programme.desc: A talented scholar, Bo Hu, is attracted by the pretty maid, Qiu Xiang. In order to get close to her and win her love, he disguises as a servant to work in the same household. Qiu Xiang does not believe Bo Hu when he discloses his true identity to her, only falling in love with him when he reveals his talents and with his friends help.

programme.title: The Merry Wife
programme.desc: A 17-year old schoolgirl marries her 35-year-old teacher. Comedy ensues when they attempt to keep their relationship a secret despite being in the same school. When they discover unwanted suitors going after their other halves, jealousy threatens to expose their marriage any minute!

programme.title: The Empress Dowager
programme.desc: Award-winning drama featuring a passionate performance by Lisa Lu, enhanced by sumptuous costumes and sets, produces a powerful, fascinating story. In five thousand years of Chinese history, there was never a more fascinating woman than the dragon lady of the Ching Dynasty, also the Empress Dowager, who was the power behind the throne for the last half of the 19th century. The vast tapestry of palace intrigues is vividly brought to the screen.

programme.title: The Twin Swords
programme.desc: Gui Wu and his wife Gan Lian Zhu are the famous Twin Swords in the martial arts world. One day, they stumble upon a kidnapping plot at the Red Lotus Temple and Lian Zhu is held captive. Wu successfully escapes to find the Gan family for help, not knowing that he is sending them into an ambush by the kidnappers. Can he finally save Lian Zhu?

programme.title: Return of the One-armed Swordsman
programme.desc: One-armed Swordsman Fang Kang wants to lead a quiet life with his wife, but when she is abducted by the Eight Demon Swordsmen clan, he is forced to take them on in order to save her.

programme.title: Ode to Gallantry
programme.desc: In this surprisingly light-hearted "Venoms" martial arts adventure, a lone wanderer is repeatedly mistaken for someone else and drawn into a number of violent battles.

programme.title: Torrent Of Desire
programme.desc: Rich playboy David is a drunk until he falls in love with a fashion model Dan Feng and marries her. David's sister Mona is in love with his best friend Han Ming, who rejected her as he secretly loves Dan Feng as well. Out of jealousy and hatred, Mona lies to David about a fake affair between Han Ming and Dan Feng...

programme.title: The Fastest Sword
programme.desc: Southern Swordsman Ting is named The Fastest Sword but is defeated by a street monk and has to fulfil his promise of working on stone craving with the monk for three years. Ting returns home to lead a peaceful life after that and declines all fight challenges. Even so, he is forced to fight the Northern Swordsman. Who will win finally?

programme.title: Return of the Phoenix
programme.desc: An imperial minister Cheng betroths his pretty younger daughter, Ye, to his friend's son, Mu. His wife however, refuses to let Ye marry before her elder daughter Yan, who is ugly and undesirable. Yan is asked to pretend as Ye to meet Mu but scares him away. A rich guy who likes Ye meanwhile pretends as Mu to attend the wedding...

programme.title: A Deadly Secret
programme.desc: A corrupt magistrate, obsessed with finding a hidden treasure, jails and tortures his daughter's lover and buries his daughter alive! Ironically, it is in her coffin that the secret to the hidden treasure is found, setting off a frenzy of destruction.

programme.title: The Magnificent Trio
programme.desc: A group of farmers who are being oppressed by the local magistrates kidnap one of the magistrates daughter in the hope of being heard by the authorities. A wandering swordsman offers his help and aiding him are two fighters who have both switched sides from being the oppressors to the oppressed. The trio fight back against the magistrates!

programme.title: Disciples of the 36th Chamber
programme.desc: In the finale of this trilogy, Gordon Liu reprises his famous role, Monk San Te, as he tries to protect Fang Shih Yu, an arrogant youth who gets into trouble with the Qing officials, and nearly lands Shaolin Temple into trouble too.

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung and the Beauty
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung meets a famous courtesan in Suzhou and in order to spend as much time as possible with her, he builds a direct underground tunnel into the Forbidden City. The emperors sudden appearances through this direct access shock his people but it is also at this time that he helps the needy and cracks the gambling business in Suzhou.

programme.title: Reincarnated Swordsman
programme.desc: A Wu Dang disciple Fu, kills the chief of Wu Dang Clan and frames it on the chiefs illegitimate child, Yun. Fu then proclaims himself the new chief and orders the killing of Yun, who vows to avenge his fathers death and learns the invincible silkworm martial arts style in order to defeat Fu.

programme.title: The Lotus Lamp
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai plays both mother and son in this lavish fable about a goddess who falls in love with a mortal scholar (Cheng Pei-pei in her debut role). Over two years in production, it was released on the first anniversary of Linda's tragic suicide.

programme.title: The New One-Armed Swordsman
programme.desc: David Chiang plays the all-new one-armed hero - a man who chops off his right arm rather than live with dishonor. When the love of his life is kidnapped and his best friend is murdered by the evil gang, it is time to battle.

programme.title: Hex after Hex
programme.desc: Hell may have no fury like a woman scorned, but hell literally, really has no wrath like a lusting ghost scorned! Cult classic director Kuei Chih-hung shoots the works with this amazing horror romance starring muscular "Venom" Lo Meng.

programme.title: The Warlord
programme.desc: A bandit became a warlord in northern China by helping Russia fight against Japan. Due to his ignorance and silly behaviour, he is seen as a joke to everyone. The warlord is finally killed by the daughter of a troupe master whom he had killed for no reason, bringing a befitting end to a traitor.

programme.title: The Snake Prince
programme.desc: The Snake Prince lives on the Snake Mountain of Kwangsi with other snakes and they have lived peacefully with humans for a thousand years. All things change however, when the Snake Prince falls in love with one of the three beauties performing a sensual rain dance in the nearby village one day, and decides to marry her at all costs...

programme.title: The Enchantress
programme.desc: Shot on the Shaws' lot in the final years of Hong Kong's greatest studio, The Enchantress tells the story of martial artists who disappear in the night! Intrigued, wanna-be detective/swordsman Feng Chi-wu (Mok Siu-chung) is determined to find out what is happening. But when Feng finds out that an evil vampire spirit (Wei Chiu-hua) is killing swordsmen, he's in for more than he bargains for... It's an outlandish fairy-tale and martial arts fantasy, where your fists and sword aren't nearly enough!

programme.title: West Chamber
programme.desc: The story is based on a famous Chinese opera. A young impoverished scholar, Zhang, is enchanted by Hong, the daughter of an influential family whom he meets in a temple. The young couple faces the threat of separation due to her familys objection, so Hongs maid secretly helps to arrange their rendezvous in the West Chamber!

programme.title: Death Duel
programme.desc: Third Master is a renowned swordsman in the martial arts world, but the constant challenges by other swordsmen compel him to fake his death and pursue a secluded life. This does not prevent others from seeking him out to challenge him however, and he is forced to return to fight his way till the end.

programme.title: Summer Heat
programme.desc: Aptly described by its original title of "Money, Sex And Love", this is a gripping drama about Judy, a woman with a rich husband as well as two lovers who happen to be brothers. Jenny Hu is Judy, and her knockout beauty makes this summer sizzle...

programme.title: Usurpers Of Emperor's Power
programme.desc: The last ruler of Tang, Li Yao is deposed by Chao Kuang-jun, the founder of the Sung Dynasty. Unfortunately his actions unleash a new plague - his brother Kuang-yi - on the courts and his people. The marauding Kuang-yi rapes and plunders. As more people get involved, it turns into a bloody battlefield of betrayal. It is up to upright officials like Li Lang to put an end to it. But can one man take on the imperial army?

programme.title: Two Champions of Shaolin
programme.desc: Set in the Qing Dynasty, the Shaolin clan wants to overthrow Qing and restore the Ming Dynasty, while the Wudang clan is backed by the Qing government. The two renowned clans eventually set themselves up against each other, and a series of vicious fighting has just begun

programme.title: Brotherhood
programme.desc: Liu serves his triad society loyally and tries to live a respectable life, but over time his good intentions lead him to an all-out gang war with a startling conclusion.

programme.title: Shaolin Rescuers
programme.desc: Hong Xi Guan of Shaolin is chased and wounded by a martial arts scum who took refuge in the Qing court. He is saved and healed by friends from the wet market and they hide Hong in a bean curd shop to protect him. However, Hongs enemy finds him and ambushes him at the shop, hoping to capture Hong and all his friends.

programme.title: The Golden Knight
programme.desc: The heroine Yu Fei Xia is accused of stealing the book of martial arts secrets. To prove her innocence, she disguises herself as a man and finds her way into the Shaolin Temple to find out the truth

programme.title: Wild Castles S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Carcassonne - Travel to a centuries-old French fortress, home to some of history's greatest empires. Carcassone, once a centre of wealth and culture, is now a haven for wildlife. Birds, wild boar, and armies of insects endure in its bountiful surroundings.

programme.title: Secret Life of the Wombat S1 Ep1
programme.desc: Wombat Wood - In the cool highlands near Australias Snowy Mountains is Wombat Wood. There, dotted amongst the trees and dense foliage, are over a hundred wombat burrows. But when some of the burrows are flooded, the wombats need to find safety.

programme.title: Wildest New Zealand S1 Ep1
programme.desc: A Tale Of Two Penguins - Waddle into the world of the little blue penguin, the planets smallest penguin species, and follow two brave young males on their diverging routes to romance. See them learn crucial survival tactics, face enemies, and overcome danger, all for love.

programme.title: Wildest New Zealand S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Untamed West - Journey along a stunning strip of New Zealands West Coast that boasts rare ecological jewels, like alpine parrots and ancient eels. Discover its astonishing array of animals, which have developed cunning and resourceful ways to survive in the wild.

programme.title: Wildest New Zealand S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Wild Fortresses - Explore two New Zealand fortresses that protect vulnerable native creatures: a moat-protected island and a hilltop citadel surrounded by a predator-proof barrier. Examine the zones thriving species, which once dominated these remote islands.

programme.title: Wildest New Zealand S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Ocean Legacy - Welcome spring on the East Coast, where the native New Zealand fur seal and northern royal albatross return to find mates, breed, and raise their young. Learn how the strongest survive despite harsh terrain, volatile weather, and peckish predators.

programme.title: Wildest New Zealand S1 Ep5
programme.desc: Creepiest Crawlies - Brave the undergrowth and discover life on a different scale. Unveil New Zealands dazzling invertebrate population and examine the remarkable lives of flesh-eating centipedes, giant nocturnal crickets, fishing spiders, hungry glow-worms, and more.

programme.title: Reef Wrecks S1 Ep5
programme.desc: Mexico's Arificial Reefs - From opportunistic pirate ships to well-armed navy vessels, the Yucatan Peninsula is home to a variety of reef wrecks. With moray eels, schools of rays, and thousands of other creatures, these sunken ships have become vibrant marine habitats.

programme.title: Macro Worlds S1 Ep1
